DIAGNOSTICS
  E0230: an arithmetic expression needs an existing row — valid only in `update`, not `create`
  E0231: `text` is not numeric — an arithmetic update expression takes int/float/decimal operands
SCHEMA
model Product  table=product
  id: Id
  qty: int
  price: decimal(10, 2)
  name: text
shape ProductRow from Product
mutation adjust_stock  ret=Product
mutation apply_markup  ret=Product
mutation bad_create  ret=Product
mutation bad_operand  ret=Product
